      "text": "Stephen C. Pepper (1891-1972) \"was an American pragmatism philosopher, the Mills Professor of Philosophy at the University of California at Berkeley\", teaching from 1919 to 1953, says  [Wikipedia](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stephen_Pepper).\n"
